## Glad to see you here! &nbsp; ![](https://visitor-badge.glitch.me/badge?page_id=saigkill.saigkill)

Hi. I'm Sascha Manns from Germany. Since 1986 im working with computers. Over the years i worked with a C64, i286, i386 and other computers. I real like to work with them. So i started programming with BASIC, then Visual Basic, Ruby, Python and now C#. I learned MySQL, MS-SQL and Intersystems Cach√®. I learned different APIs and technologies and loved to learn anything new.
